{"title":"ubantu怎么让ll不显示隐藏文件","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.029Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/ubantu怎么让ll不显示隐藏文件","updated":"2023-07-28T09:18:12.202Z","content":"<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在文件中找到</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">alias</span> ll=’<span class=\"built_in\">ls</span> -alF’</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>将其改成</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">alias</span> ll=’<span class=\"built_in\">ls</span> -lF’</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后按esc键，输入<code>:wq</code>保存退出。<br>\n命令行输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时ll就不会显示隐藏文件。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Windows安装Python环境","link":"2023/07/28/Windows安装Python环境"},"next":{"title":"ubuntu22.04安装vue","link":"2023/07/28/ubuntu22.04安装vue"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/ubantu怎么让ll不显示隐藏文件/","reading_time":"55 字约 1 分钟"}